        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p><code class="inline">fun fresh_crl/2</code> will be used as input option <code class="inline">update_crl</code> to
<a href="../../../../lib/public_key/doc/html/public_key.html#pkix_crls_validate/3"><code class="inline">public_key:pkix_crls_validate/3</code></a>.</p></div>

    </div>


      <div class="summary-row">
